No way (out) - Drum and Bass meets classical music! @camokrooked meets Johann Strauss - @miralukovacs as special guest live on stage at Red Bull Symphonic Johann Strauss 2025 Edition at @donauinselfest_wien! 🎶

#redbull #verleihtflügel #redbullsymphonic #johannstrauss2025 #dif25

What happens when you turn Strauss into Drum & Bass? Tens of thousands showed up at @donauinselfest_wien to find out.

@camokrooked joined forces with the @viennasymphony and conductor Christian Kolonovits to flip the legacy of Johann Strauss. With over 60 musicians on stage and special guests @cristinapasaroiu and @miralukovacs adding their own sonic layers.

Swipe through for highlights 👉

We’re doing it again.
📍 Wiener Konzerthaus
📅 September 18 & 19
⚠️ Both shows already sold out.
